summary.ar: اختيار مثالي للطقس البارد والأيّام الشّتوية، معطف أنيق بأكمام طويلة ذات أساور مطّاطيّة مع تفاصيل رباط على الخصر وزر إغلاق تؤمن لك ارتداءا ملائما. كما يتمتّع بتفاصيل مخمليّة تزيدك أنوثةً. هذا المعطف أنيق ولا غنى عن اقتنائه.
summary.en: An ideal pick for cold weather, this overcoat has plush detailed hem and cuffed sleeves for additional warmth and a snazzy style. It has long sleeves and is secured with tie-up detail at the waist along with button closure to ensure a snug and warm fit. Featuring a solid design, this jacket is a must-have to make a statement.

summary.en: Well-enriched with the dainty floral print, this jacket by Rina is a must-have in your wardrobe. The elasticated detail across the cuff of the three-quarter sleeves and hem give a smart design highlight to this piece while the round neck and zip closure in front add to its main feature. Moreover, tailor-made from quality fabric, this lightweight jacket offers prolonged comfort.
